    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_002/002",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "MolNetEnhancer is a software package available in Python and R that unites the output of several metabolome mining and annotation tools, including mass spectral molecular networking through GNPS, unsupervised substructure discovery through MS2LDA and in silico structure annotation, for example through NAP, DEREPLICATOR, or SIRIUS+CSI:FingerID (Figure 1).",
