      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Where tandem mass spectral molecular networking efficiently can group molecular features in molecular families [10], MS2LDA can discover substructures, not only based on common fragment peaks but also common neutral losses, which can aid in further annotation of subfamilies and shared modifications",
