      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The MolNetEnhancer workflow results in one graphml network file that contains all the structural information obtained from the individual tools. Such a file can be easily imported into network visualization tools such as Cytoscape [31], an environment where additional metadata on the molecular features can be added.",
