      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Perform mass spectral molecular networking analysis through the Global Natural Products Social Molecular Networking platform (https://gnps.ucsd.edu)... The workflow enhances the currently available molecular networking methods based on either MS-Cluster [29] (classical) or MZmine2 [30] (also called 'feature-based molecular networking')... results in annotated molecular networks that can be explored in Cytoscape [31].",
