      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "MolNetEnhancer is a software package available in Python and R that unites the output of several metabolome mining and annotation tools... MolNetEnhancer is freely available on GitHub at https://github.com/madeleineernst/pyMolNetEnhancer and https://github.com/madeleineernst/RMolNetEnhancer.",
